--- !u!114 &850890613
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 850890612}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 21c58ebed6a8b304bbd5737f7bdb4807, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  lines:
  - speakerName: Commander
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: You found a computer?
    choices: []
    nextLineIndex: 0
  - speakerName: Commander
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "And there\u2019s a big security door next to it?"
    choices: []
    nextLineIndex: 1
  - speakerName: Commander
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Hold on\u2026 give me a second."
    choices: []
    nextLineIndex: 2
  - speakerName: Commander
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "I\u2019m in."
    choices: []
    nextLineIndex: 3
  - speakerName: Commander
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "\u2026Okay. I see it."
    choices: []
    nextLineIndex: 4
  - speakerName: Commander
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "The briefcase is behind that door. But it\u2019s locked."
    choices: []
    nextLineIndex: 5
  - speakerName: Commander
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: It needs a keycard. And not just any keycard.
    choices: []
    nextLineIndex: 6
  - speakerName: Commander
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Only a high-ranking officer carries it.
    choices: []
    nextLineIndex: 7
  - speakerName: Commander
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Alright. Here\u2019s what we\u2019re going to do."
    choices: []
    nextLineIndex: 8
  - speakerName: Commander
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "I\u2019ll trigger the alarms To get their attention."
    choices: []
    nextLineIndex: 9
  - speakerName: Commander
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: But just in case, I want you to get close to the other 3 computers in the
      building.
    choices: []
    nextLineIndex: 10
  - speakerName: Commander
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "When you\u2019re near them, I can hack them remotely."
    choices: []
    nextLineIndex: 11
  - speakerName: Commander
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: If we cause enough trouble, someone important will come check it out.
    choices: []
    nextLineIndex: 12
  - speakerName: Commander
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Before I start the alarms\u2026"
    choices: []
    nextLineIndex: 13
  - speakerName: Commander
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Good luck.
    choices: []
    nextLineIndex: -1
